OL,3,CMore than 300,000 cancer patients face
OL,4,CNHS delays 'unless action is taken'
OL,6,FMore than 300,000 cancer patients will
OL,7,Fface delays in their treatment over
OL,8,Fthe next five years, unless the NHS is
OL,9,Fgiven the resources it needs,
OL,10,Faccording to new figures.
OL,12,FBreast Cancer UK has projected that
OL,13,Fbetween now and 2029, more than
OL,14,F301,000 people diagnosed with the
OL,15,Fdisease will not get the treatment
OL,16,Fthey need within NHS waiting time
OL,17,Ftargets.
