OL,3,CMore than 300,000 cancer patients face
OL,4,CNHS delays 'unless action is taken'
OL,6,FThe charity also found that patients
OL,7,Fare waiting too long to be diagnosed
OL,8,Fin the first place, because of staff
OL,9,Fshortages and lack of equipment.
OL,11,FCancer Research chief executive
OL,12,FMichelle Mitchell, said: "Hardworking
OL,13,Fstaff across the NHS are treating more
OL,14,Fpatients in England than ever before,
OL,15,Fbut this data provides a stark warning
OL,16,Fto the UK Government."
OL,18,FShe said the NHS "does not have the
OL,19,Frequired resources to cope" with the
OL,20,Frecord numbers of people being
OL,21,Fdiagnosed with cancer in the UK.
