OL,3,CMore than 300,000 cancer patients face
OL,4,CNHS delays 'unless action is taken'
OL,6,F"Unless action is taken, things could
OL,7,Fbe even worse in five years' time,"
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,FCancer Research UK welcomed the
OL,11,Fgovernment's pledge to meet cancer
OL,12,Fwait time targets by the end of this
OL,13,FParliament, but stressed that long-
OL,14,Fterm planning was required to provide
OL,15,Fthe NHS with the equipment and staff
OL,16,Fit needs.
