OL,3,CMore than 300,000 cancer patients face
OL,4,CNHS delays 'unless action is taken'
OL,6,FClaire Rowney, chief executive of
OL,7,FBreast Cancer Now, said: "These latest
OL,8,Fbleak figures emphasise a devastating
OL,9,F'new normal' of long waits for people
OL,10,Fto get a cancer diagnosis and start
OL,11,Fvital treatment that gives them the
OL,12,Fbest chance of survival."
OL,14,FShe said the government's upcoming 10-
OL,15,Fyear plan for health must include
OL,16,F"ambitious, long-term solutions to
OL,17,Ftackle the issues being faced by
OL,18,Fcancer patients and ensure it's backed
OL,19,Fby a fully-funded and staffed
OL,20,Fworkforce."
